    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Bash your<strong> lemongrass </strong>with a<strong> rolling pin</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>sweet potato[es]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1688641283525-x200.jpg",
