            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based, <strong>hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> onion wedges </strong>and <strong>bashed lemongrass</strong> to the pot with the <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1688641288757-x200.jpg",
