    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 25 min, remove the dish from the oven</p><p>Add your <strong>udon noodles </strong>(making sure they're fully submerged)<strong> </strong>and top with your <strong>mooli slaw mix</strong></p><p>Cover with a lid and return the dish to the oven for 5-7 min further or until the noodles are tender – this is your <strong>one-pot creamy sweet potato laksa udon</strong></p><p>Once tender, gently separate the noodles with a fork</p>",
